  section
    h2 Arrays
    p.fragment An array is an ordered collection of references to other types.

  section
    h2 Array Example
    pre
      code.javascript.
        var arr = [];

        // Add item to end (PUSH)
        arr.push('hello');
        console.log(arr);

        // Get length of array
        console.log(arr.length);

        // Pop item off end
        var item = arr.pop();
        console.log(item);
        console.log(arr.length);

