    h2 Objects
    p.fragment Objects are like classes in other languages. Not everything is the same though.

  section
    h2 Objects are Key - Value pairs
    p.fragment Objects can be though of as a map from a key to a value. Much like a dictionary in Python.
    pre.fragment
      code.javascript.
        var someObj = {
          hello: 'World',
          foo: 'bar',
        };

        console.log(someObj['hello']);
        console.log(someObj['abc']);

  section
    h2 Objects as Classes
    p.fragment Objects can also act like a class
    pre.fragment
      code.javascript.
        function Rectangle(width, height) {
          this.width = width;
          this.height = height;
          
          this.area = function () {
            return this.width * this.height;
          };
